name: Alfred Scott
description: I am outgoing with a great sense of humor. I am very affectionate who still believes in chivalry. I love music ranging from the blues, rock and classical. I also enjoy reading a wide variety of books. I am looking for someone who has similar taste, but can introduce me to new things. Laughing, being affectionate and easy going would be great with me. I am looking forward to a new chapter in my life.
